item.title: CVE-2023-29081|2024-08-02T14:00:15.129Z -- revenera -- installshield
item.description: A vulnerability has been reported in Suite Setups built with versions prior to InstallShield 2023 R2. This vulnerability may allow locally authenticated users to cause a Denial of Service (DoS) condition when handling move operations on local, temporary folders.
